Package org.apache.drill.metastore.expressions

package org.apache.drill.metastore.expressions
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.apache.drill.metastore
     
  • Class
    Description
    DoubleExpressionPredicate
    Indicates double expression predicate implementations.
    DoubleExpressionPredicate.And
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.AND operator expression: storagePlugin = 'dfs' and workspace = 'tmp'.
    DoubleExpressionPredicate.Or
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.OR operator expression: storagePlugin = 'dfs' or storagePlugin = 's3'.
    FilterExpression
    Interface which defines filter expression types by which Metastore data can be read or deleted.
    FilterExpression.Operator
    Indicates list of supported operators that can be used in filter expressions.
    FilterExpression.Visitor<T>
    Transforms FilterExpression implementations into suitable for Metastore implementation representation.
    IsPredicate
    Indicates IS predicate implementations.
    IsPredicate.IsNotNull
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.IS_NOT_NULL operator expression: storagePlugin is not null.
    IsPredicate.IsNull
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.IS_NULL operator expression: storagePlugin is null.
    ListPredicate<T>
    Indicates list predicate implementations which have column and list of values.
    ListPredicate.In<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.IN operator expression: storagePlugin in ('dfs', 's3').
    ListPredicate.NotIn<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.NOT_IN operator expression: storagePlugin not in ('dfs', 's3').
    SimplePredicate<T>
    Indicates simple predicate implementations which have column and one value.
    SimplePredicate.Equal<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.EQUAL operator expression: storagePlugin = 'dfs'.
    SimplePredicate.GreaterThan<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.GREATER_THAN operator expression: index > 1.
    SimplePredicate.GreaterThanOrEqual<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUAL operator expression: index >= 1.
    SimplePredicate.LessThan<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.LESS_THAN operator expression: index < 1.
    SimplePredicate.LessThanOrEqual<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.LESS_THAN_OR_EQUAL operator expression: index <= 1.
    SimplePredicate.NotEqual<T>
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.NOT_EQUAL operator expression: storagePlugin != 'dfs'.
    SingleExpressionPredicate
    Indicates single expression predicate implementations.
    SingleExpressionPredicate.Not
    Indicates FilterExpression.Operator.NOT operator expression: not(storagePlugin = 'dfs').
